"""
PART II Entitlement and amount

4A. Meaning of “qualifying young person”

(1)

(b)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

A person who has reached the age of 16 but not the age of 20 is a qualifying young person for the purposes of these Regulations—

up to, but not including, the 1st September following the person's 19th birthday, if the person is enrolled on, or accepted for, approved training or a course of education—

(iii)

where the average time spent during term time in receiving tuition, engaging in practical work or supervised study or taking examinations exceeds 12 hours per week.
"""

qualifying_young_person_minimum_age_16:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Integer
    from 2025-03-21:
        16

qualifying_young_person_maximum_age_20:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Integer
    from 2025-03-21:
        20

qualifying_young_person_september_following_birthday_age_19:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Integer
    from 2025-03-21:
        19

qualifying_young_person_term_time_hours_threshold_12:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Integer
    from 2025-03-21:
        12

person_age_years:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Integer

person_is_enrolled_on_or_accepted_for_approved_training_or_course_of_education:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

period_is_up_to_but_not_including_1st_september_following_persons_19th_birthday:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

average_term_time_hours_in_tuition_practical_work_supervised_study_or_examinations_per_week:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Float

qualifying_young_person_4A_1_b_iii:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        person_age_years >= qualifying_young_person_minimum_age_16 and person_age_years < qualifying_young_person_maximum_age_20 and period_is_up_to_but_not_including_1st_september_following_persons_19th_birthday and person_is_enrolled_on_or_accepted_for_approved_training_or_course_of_education and average_term_time_hours_in_tuition_practical_work_supervised_study_or_examinations_per_week > qualifying_young_person_term_time_hours_threshold_12
